<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" %>
<%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/include/taglib.jsp"%>
<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<meta name="decorator" content="help_center"/>
	<link href="${ctxStatic}/modules/front/css/help_center.css?${version }" rel="stylesheet"/>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<div id="content_bottom" class="help_content">
	<div class="help_main">
        <div class="right_title"><span>债权转让</span></div>
    	<div class="content">
            <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
            
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>什么是债权转让？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>指债权持有人通过花生金服债权转让平台将债权挂出且与购买人签订债权转让协议，将所持有的债权转让给购买人的操作。<a href="" class="btn_text_gold">查看详情>></a>。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>什么样的债权可以转让？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>没有处于逾期状态的债权可随时进行转让。</p>
                    <p><span class="label label-important">注：</span> 如果债权转让挂出时没有处于逾期，但在转让途中时债权变为逾期状态，系统将会停止债权转让。</p>
                    <p><span class="label label-important">注：</span> 明确不允许转让的项目不可以转让债权。</p>
                    <p><span class="label label-important">注：</span> 债权持有期到期前1个月内，不可以转让债权。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>购买待转让的债权有什么好处？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>购买待转让的债权有什么好处</p>
                    <p>1.收益更高，除待收利息，更有本金折价的收益；<br>2.安全性更高，逾期可能性较低；<br>3.投资回收更快，债权的剩余期数更少。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>如何转出债权提前收回投资？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>当您持有的债权处于可转让状态时，您可以打开【我的花生金服】--【投资管理】--【我的债权】--【持有中】页面进行债权转让操作。<a href="" class="btn_text_gold">查看操作流程>></a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>如何买入转让债权？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>您可以在债权转让项目页面进行购买债权。<a href="" class="btn_text_gold">查看操作流程>></a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse7" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>债权转让管理费如何收取？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>平台向转出人和购买人同时收取债权转让管理费。</p>
                    <p><strong>转让管理费金额：成交金额*转让管理费率。</strong>转让管理费按转让债权金额的0.2%收取，债权转让管理费在成交后直接从成交金额中扣除，不成交不收费。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse8" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>申请转让的债权一定能够成功转让出去吗？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>债权交易平台仅为债权转让者和投资人提供中介服务，并不承诺为每一个债权转让者都能成功转让。因此转让人有债权无法成功转让的风险。一般情况下，转让债权都能在较短时间内达成转让交易。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse9" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>提出债权转让申请后是否可以撤回？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>提出债权转让申请后是否可以撤回</p>
                    <p>在“债权交易”页面内上部点击“转让中”，即可看到可撤销的待转让债权项目。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse10" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>什么情况下待转让债权会自动失效？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>三种情况下待转让债权会自动失效：</p>
                    <p>1.到达转让者设定的价格有效期；<br>2.本息发生变化，即融资人按时或提前还款；<br>3.原始标的发生逾期。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse11" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>债权是否可以部分转让？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse11" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>花生金服平台不允许部分转让债权，债权必须全部转让。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
	function collapseClick(element) {
		if($(element).hasClass("collapsed")) {
			$(element).find("i").removeClass("icon_plus").addClass("icon_minus");
		}else {
			$(element).find("i").removeClass("icon_minus").addClass("icon_plus");
		}
	}
</script>
</body>
</html>
